Another strategy to move away from fossil fuels is to select electric-based heating technologies. One mature technology already fully integrated in pyrometallurgy are electric arc furnaces33 as highlighted in “Electric arc furnaces” section. The operating parameters of EAF furnaces are now being optimized via AI and machine learning,234 which are other tools to reduce CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
